        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a">
                Mr. Lloyd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-12-05/debates/60235de6-44ed-423f-9923-484c1aba3322/NationalCoalBoard(SirEYoungSResignation)#contribution-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Am I right in thinking that following the resignation of Sir Charles Reid and now the resignation of Sir Eric Young, there is at present no mining engineer as a member of the National Coal Board?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-12-05/debates/60235de6-44ed-423f-9923-484c1aba3322/NationalCoalBoard(SirEYoungSResignation)#contribution-5d3f18a6-260e-4c1b-aed3-c7b61477611a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
                Mr. Noel-Baker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-12-05/debates/60235de6-44ed-423f-9923-484c1aba3322/NationalCoalBoard(SirEYoungSResignation)#contribution-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">That is true at this moment. Of course, it is desirable, in principle, that there should be a mining engineer on the National Coal Board. The right hon. Gentleman will remember that the National Coal Board is not now functional in character, and that it has at its disposal nearly all the able mining engineers in the country.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-12-05/debates/60235de6-44ed-423f-9923-484c1aba3322/NationalCoalBoard(SirEYoungSResignation)#contribution-c5ae6983-4f97-4ebe-8b89-7540bf7552a6">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





